trust you anymore.

442
01:06:11,735 --> 01:06:13,568
You have to move on, Lucinda.

443
01:06:13,570 --> 01:06:17,072
- I Can't control it, mom.
- I know you can.

444
01:06:17,074 --> 01:06:19,207
- I Can't.
- Yes...

445
01:06:20,610 --> 01:06:21,676
You can.

446
01:06:21,678 --> 01:06:23,478
Your other spirits...

447
01:06:23,480 --> 01:06:26,014
