460
01:07:25,175 --> 01:07:26,775
I love you, mom.

461
01:07:26,777 --> 01:07:28,576
I love you, too.

462
01:07:32,816 --> 01:07:36,718
Is that Tess?

463
01:07:36,720 --> 01:07:38,553
I'm not sure.

464
01:07:38,555 --> 01:07:40,555
You have to try harder, Lucy.
Is that Tess?

465
01:08:00,077 --> 01:08:02,744
<i>- What's going on?</i>
